Iceland (Bing dao ) u sakahenulan a tu se u Reykjavik, u satabakiay aca nu Bing daoa tu se, kahenulan a tu se tapiingan nu satipan timulan a kakitizaan mahamin u tademaw nu kanatal tulu hun a tusa.
